OL,5, Glasgow City Council has passed a      
OL,6, motion requiring hospitality businesses
OL,7, to provide free and safe transport home
OL,8, for late night workers after 23:00.    
OL,10,FIt will apply to any new alcohol       
OL,11,Flicences, or existing businesses       
OL,12,Fapplying for extended operating hours. 
OL,14,FUnite union members had lobbied for the
OL,15,Fmove through the Get Me Home Safely    
OL,16,Fcampaign.                              
OL,18,FIt was led by hotel worker Caitlin Lee 
OL,19,Fwho was sexually assaulted as she was  
OL,20,Fwalking home after finishing her shift.
